raw_data.title: Technical Specialist
raw_data.description: Works with other stakeholders within the project to coordinate and create requisite deliverables to meet requirements and deadlines by developing, implementing and maintaining project policies and procedures.   Implements project scheduling, engineering, procurement and cost management procedures, deployment and management of  information systems, computer related equipment and software for the team.

raw_data.title: Technical Specialist , Sr
raw_data.description: Plans, organizes, and coordinates the activities of personnel engaged in the project.   Controls and reviews work to ensure timeliness and accuracy of responsible functions.  Establishes and maintains schedule for the group to be consistent with budgetary and time constraints.  Assists employees with problem resolution and assures compliance with clients policies, procedures and requirements. Develops innovative approaches to non-routine, nonrecurring work requests based on expertise and knowledge. Performs any other related duties as may be required to meet objectives of the group; including training.

raw_data.title: Consultant
raw_data.description: Supports and helps direct the completion of project specific tasks within estimated time frames and budget constraints.  Works closely with clients to define goals and objectives and performs tasks with minimal guidance.  Experienced analytical and consulting skills, guiding  staff and able to work effectively within a team environment or independently.  Develops implementation  plans based on industry best practices, and reviews them  with  the responsible  decision  makers.  Brings  successful experience in consultative roles and proven skills in achieving positive improvements in customer operations.

raw_data.title: Consultant, Sr.
raw_data.description: Directs the completion of project specific tasks within estimated time frames and budget constraints while defining and executing activities within a project including planning, scoping, interviewing, data analysis,  project management, test and validation and other related tasks.  Responsibilities include engagement planning, supervision, review and completion of work.  Demonstrated ability to provide guidance and direction for project specific tasks and monitors the status of the project  and advises and consults with senior management . raw_data.title: Project Manager
raw_data.description: Manages assigned project(s) in accordance with the requirements of the contract between the company and the client, execution of the work in accordance with the quality standards and requirements specified for the project, serves as the key point of contact with the client on project execution, budget, and schedule.  Experience in project development life cycle phases from inception to deployment, with an ability to provide guidance and direction in these tasks areas is required
